lead_paragraph: Shanshan Feng won back-to-back tournaments for the first time in her career after the world number eight survived a late scare to secure a one-stroke victory over South Korea's Jang Ha-na at the co-sanctioned Japan Classic on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Golf: In-Form Feng Holds On to Claim Japan Classic Title
